   Employees> Hiring Employees
     __________________________________________________________________


   Men shaking hands. As your business begins to succeed, one of the first
   things you will need to do is hire employees. This section provides
   information about finding, hiring, and training employees, recording
   their social security numbers, determining wage withholding, and
   determining whether those assisting you with routine housework are
   household employees.

